Description:
Pandora: First Contact - a sci-fi turn based strategy game that unfolds in the future where mankind has discovered a new Earth-like planet , called Pandora .
Its surface contains a variety of eco- regions: from ice land in the north and ending with lush tropical forests in the south. But not without its dangers in the face of predators , deadly bugs and giant creatures that inhabit the ocean depths
